customProperties.view_definition:
SELECT sensor_data.location,
    count(DISTINCT sensor_data.device_id) AS device_count,
    avg(sensor_data.temperature) AS avg_temperature,
    avg(sensor_data.humidity) AS avg_humidity
   FROM sensor_data
  WHERE (sensor_data."time" > (now() - '1 day'::interval))
  GROUP BY sensor_data.location;

customProperties.view_definition:
SELECT h.hour,
    h.location,
    h.avg_temperature,
    h.avg_humidity,
    h.sample_count,
        CASE
            WHEN (h.avg_temperature > (25)::double precision) THEN 'Hot'::text
            WHEN (h.avg_temperature < (15)::double precision) THEN 'Cold'::text
            ELSE 'Moderate'::text
        END AS temp_category
   FROM sensor_hourly_avg h
  WHERE (h.hour > (now() - '24:00:00'::interval));

SELECT
  sensor_data.location,
  COUNT(DISTINCT sensor_data.device_id) AS device_count,
  AVG(sensor_data.temperature) AS avg_temperature,
  AVG(sensor_data.humidity) AS avg_humidity
FROM sensor_data
WHERE
  (
    sensor_data."time" > (
      CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - CAST('1 day' AS INTERVAL)
    )
  )
GROUP BY
  sensor_data.location

SELECT
  h.hour,
  h.location,
  h.avg_temperature,
  h.avg_humidity,
  h.sample_count,
  CASE
    WHEN (
      h.avg_temperature > CAST((
        25
      ) AS DOUBLE PRECISION)
    )
    THEN CAST('Hot' AS TEXT)
    WHEN (
      h.avg_temperature < CAST((
        15
      ) AS DOUBLE PRECISION)
    )
    THEN CAST('Cold' AS TEXT)
    ELSE CAST('Moderate' AS TEXT)
  END AS temp_category
FROM sensor_hourly_avg AS h
WHERE
  (
    h.hour > (
      CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - CAST('24:00:00' AS INTERVAL)
    )
  )
